## ğŸ§ª Testing

To run the tests, use the following command:

```sh
pytest tests/
```

## Installation

pip:

```sh
pip install schore
```

If you use [uv](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) as your Python package manager:

```sh
uv add schore
```

